{"tid":2112252,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"「搞笑」毒撚對異性做過嘅柒事","createTime":"2020-07-17T07:22:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-21T04:34:38.000Z","uid":362865,"like":4,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"236272d150b66dd31ea32561df03b8fd21685df6","tid":2112252,"uid":362865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T07:22:02.000Z","msg":"入門級:<br />\n1. 同女仔傾傾下,同佢講「你不如問下你啲朋友點睇」,然後口快快補多句「你有朋友嗰可?」<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 去交流識左一個好動漫正太樣嘅日本人, 佢勁有禮貌又成日一齊打波, 一齊返學放學, 兩個月後有日見佢同班女行入女廁, 問下冇入廁所嘅女同學先知佢係女仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n3. 食完飯夾錢, 我拎住張500蚊,諗住同人夾, 然後望住個女仔問:「喂, 你幾錢?」。 當時眾人表情- <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n4. 有個交換生唔舒服, 好痛苦咁瞓左喺醫療室到, 我入去幫佢較較冷氣拎左張被比佢順便問候一兩句。 點知下兩堂見到佢都take左我呢堂, 然後不停同同鄉講話我好好人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。 我行到佢後面佢都仲未知, 佢啲同鄉笑淫淫咁望住佢後面嘅我, 當佢話:「可以再見到佢就好」嗰陣拉長個好字咁轉頭望到我。 然後一巴車落黎尖叫衝左出課室<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有好多,睇情況再update下當笑話<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"277c228540fafd17baf927c12e340ec271c3ffdd","tid":2112252,"uid":360830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T07:24:00.000Z","msg":"3係玩家級<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06d070fd83e5f9b98cbdb42cb8bd9843db063ef8","tid":2112252,"uid":38691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T07:24:21.000Z","msg":"ff"},{"pid":"6c8079aa2138966741b68cbf1c55afec1ff0c30a","tid":2112252,"uid":362865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"277c228540fafd17b